Personality & Social Habits Dataset

Personality traits such as extroversion and introversion shape how individuals interact with their social environments. This dataset offers insights into behaviors like time spent alone, social event attendance, and social media engagement, making it suitable for fields like psychology, sociology, marketing, and machine learning. Whether you are predicting personality types or analyzing social patterns, this dataset is your gateway to interesting insights.
